OL,3,CMPs face 'tough decision' in vote to
OL,4,Ccut winter fuel allowance for
OL,5,Cpensioners
OL,7,FMPs will vote today on a controversial
OL,8,Fplan to cut the winter fuel payment
OL,9,Ffor most pensioners after the prime
OL,10,Fminister recognised it will be a
OL,11,F"really tough decision".
OL,13,FAround 10 million pensioners will lose
OL,14,Ftheir eligibility for the annual tax-
OL,15,Ffree winter fuel payment of #200 or
OL,16,F#300, a change justified by Sir Keir
OL,17,FStarmer to "secure the foundations" of
OL,18,Fthe economy.
