OL,3,CMPs face 'tough decision' in vote to
OL,4,Ccut winter fuel allowance for
OL,5,Cpensioners
OL,7,FThe decision has sparked backlash from
OL,8,Fbackbench MPs, union leaders, and the
OL,9,Fopposition, who have all urged the
OL,10,Fgovernment to reverse course. It could
OL,11,Flead to a potential backbench revolt
OL,12,Fin today's Commons vote.
OL,14,FChancellor Rachel Reeves announced the
OL,15,Fcuts in July as part of a series of
OL,16,Fmeasures to address the #22 billion
OL,17,F"black hole" in public finances left
OL,18,Fby the previous Tory government.
