OL,3,CMPs face 'tough decision' in vote to
OL,4,Ccut winter fuel allowance for
OL,5,Cpensioners
OL,7,FThe prime minister told journalists on
OL,8,FMonday: "Let me first recognise this a
OL,9,Freally tough decision that we've had
OL,10,Fto make."
OL,12,FHe added Labour had been "elected into
OL,13,Fgovernment on the basis of economic
OL,14,Fstability, that we would secure the
OL,15,Ffoundations".
