OL,3,CMPs face 'tough decision' in vote to
OL,4,Ccut winter fuel allowance for
OL,5,Cpensioners
OL,7,F"If you're asking whether I recognise
OL,8,Fit's a tough decision I absolutely
OL,9,Frecognise the tough decision. If
OL,10,Fyou're asking, would I want to make
OL,11,Fthis decision, the answer is no, but I
OL,12,Fdid not want to inherit a #22 billion
OL,13,Fblack hole, and I'm not prepared to
OL,14,Fwalk past that," he said.
OL,16,FAround 17 Labour MPs have now signed a
OL,17,Fmotion put forward by Neil Duncan-
OL,18,FJordan calling on the Government to
OL,19,Fdelay implementing the cut.
