OL,7,FThe motion has also been backed by six
OL,8,Fof the seven MPs who lost the party
OL,9,Fwhip in July after voting against the
OL,10,FKing's Speech, in protest of the
OL,11,FGovernment's refusal to scrap the two-
OL,12,Fchild benefit cap.
OL,14,FBusiness Secretary Jonathan Reynolds
OL,15,Furged Labour MPs to back the
OL,16,FGovernment's plans.
