OL,7,FSpeaking on Times Radio, he said:
OL,8,F"Fixing the foundations of the country
OL,9,Fisn't just about difficult things like
OL,10,Fthis, which are decisions that ideally
OL,11,Fyou wouldn't have to make. It's about
OL,12,Fhow you get to a better future."
OL,14,FA Number 10 spokeswoman said there was
OL,15,Fno disagreement among ministers over
OL,16,Fthe planned cut during Monday's
OL,17,FCabinet meeting.
