OL,7,FThe change is expected to reduce the
OL,8,Fnumber of eligible pensioners from
OL,9,F11.4 million to 1.5 million, with most
OL,10,Fof those remaining on pension credit.
OL,11,FThis is expected to save around #1.4
OL,12,Fbillion this year.
