OL,3,CMPs face 'tough decision' in vote to
OL,4,Ccut winter fuel allowance for
OL,5,Cpensioners
OL,7,FUnite union general secretary Sharon
OL,8,FGraham has accused Labour of "picking
OL,9,Fthe pocket of pensioners" and called
OL,10,Ffor a wealth tax to raise funds
OL,11,Finstead.
OL,13,FThe Prime Minister said that measures
OL,14,Fto stabilise the economy are "the
OL,15,Ffoundation for the triple lock, which
OL,16,Fin the end means that the state
OL,17,Fpension will increase in a way that
OL,18,Foutstrips the winter fuel payment".
