OL,7,FThe Chancellor wrote in The Telegraph
OL,8,Fon Monday that the Treasury estimates
OL,9,Fmaintaining the triple lock will make
OL,10,Fa state pension worth around #1,700
OL,11,Fmore by 2029.
OL,13,FThe triple lock guarantees the state
OL,14,Fpension will rise each year by the
OL,15,Fhighest of either inflation, wage
OL,16,Fincreases or 2.5%.
